{"tid":560272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"收酬60萬洩謀殺案機密 兩警分別囚3年及2年半","createTime":"2018-02-14T02:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T10:05:20.000Z","uid":136994,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"de6ded4804524aba691f1bc23d0d90ffbfd1cd80","tid":560272,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:59:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180214/57831480?_ga=2.146499188.1103941901.1518576967-575505850.1502150827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F57831480%3F_ga%3D2.146499188.1103941901.1518576967-575505850.1502150827&d=nZ3leCUZjns4JbAcFq8YcE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=17671c85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F57831480%3F_ga%3D2.146499188.1103941901.1518576967-575505850.1502150827&h=3881b156\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180214/57831480?_ga=2.146499188.1103941901.1518576967-575505850.1502150827</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180214/large/1518574930_d6a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180214%2Flarge%2F1518574930_d6a6.jpg&h=b3206b4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警署警長及警員涉將黑幫仇殺案的閉路電視、法證結果及疑犯名單等機密資料賣給任中間人的商人，又教路潛逃疑犯返港時應「打死都唔好認」，又稱會將所有證據「撳X晒」，以賺取60萬元報酬。兩警及商人早前被裁定串謀公職人員行為失當罪，警長今被判囚兩年半、警員入獄3年，商人則入獄2年3個月。<br />\n<br />\n3名被告依次是警員李潤福（47歲）、警署警長葉國良（50歲）及商人洪偉明（46歲）。<br />\n案情指，警方於2014年調查一宗黑幫仇殺案期間，兩名警員答應以60萬元向幕後人士提供警方調查機密資料，包括謀殺案調查進度，及潛逃疑犯應何時回港等，並教路疑犯調查時應對，應「打死都唔好認」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一年前有七警入冊<br />\n今日又有兩件洩密黑警入冊<br />\n情人節果然係警隊吉日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ac68c809753881b3e8910e6a0cfc800a4fc56a","tid":560272,"uid":10621,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T03:01:04.000Z","msg":"其實咁都判三年係咪算少 我覺得個性質好嚴重wo"},{"pid":"dcac9ed811428d83eb98377d636b93121a5e3d39","tid":560272,"uid":25794,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"20ac68c809753881b3e8910e6a0cfc800a4fc56a","tid":560272,"uid":10621,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T03:01:04.000Z","msg":"其實咁都判三年係咪算少 我覺得個性質好嚴重wo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T03:10:13.000Z","msg":"知法犯法罪減一等"},{"pid":"85c1375a4b4a3cd1dc03f79afa986b1fc1b452b8","tid":560272,"uid":153412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T03:11:08.000Z","msg":"坐咁少⋯"},{"pid":"d71c7f2344073cfddf60d9ed24abf683c8f67453","tid":560272,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T03:14:52.000Z","msg":"幫人殺人脫罪坐咁少"},{"pid":"e7f0e69c0249d38a9ec628a857ea9e8942d64655","tid":560272,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T03:17:04.000Z","msg":"巨輪陳展鵬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847c3b7ea96e9e45269e243679db34a06a0731b3","tid":560272,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T03:20:36.000Z","msg":"搭單問下，柒警上訴打甩機會有幾大？"},{"pid":"7eb1bcab9a030cd2fcc49aa93f7f203830757467","tid":560272,"uid":3039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T03:21:11.000Z","msg":"坐咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc0962b05cb4f7121a1dc6e739807f47eda142a","tid":560272,"uid":89032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T03:45:42.000Z","msg":"七驚判咁少之後我都覺得驚犬犯法都會照判少啲"},{"pid":"51731ba28d9bb2a32bced3b8d5cdf021c5662e76","tid":560272,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T08:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/2-05-2018/jG4sBN.gif\" data